Class EncryptUserServiceImpl

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.example.demo.service.serviceImpl.EncryptUserServiceImpl
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    EncryptUserService

    @Service
public class EncryptUserServiceImpl
extends java.lang.Object
implements EncryptUserService
    This class is used for mainly Encoding and Decoding the User as well as Adding Users. This class contains four methods 1.Add Users:which mainly used for adding/saving user in database. 2.Encode User: This method used for Encoding Users. 3.Decode User: This method used for Decoding Users. 4.Find User: This method is used to search list of users based on given keywords.
